metadata.description:
AMÉLIE - Mysterious, sexy, mother, economist...


To be a woman is to love tenderly and fight bravely.
It's to be tranquility in the midst of restlessness.
It's to live with sensitivity and the force of a hurricane. 
All women are strong, some just haven't discovered that yet. 

Light and Dark. Dark and Light. 
The essence of every woman.
